error.name: error
error.title: Error
error.description:
One of the following error codes:

- `requestFailed`: Thrown if the entire request failed due to e.g. CORS issues or no network connectivity.
- `serverError`: Thrown if the server returned an error response.
- `resourceNotFound`: Thrown if the resouce you are trying to get is not found.
- `unknown`: Thrown if an unknown error occurred while fetching the record.
- `responseMustBeObject`: Thrown if the server does not return an object as a response for a single data record request.

props.content: I offer 5 different workouts per week, to see the different types and times take a look at the schedule page.

props.label: View Workout Schedule and On Demand  Content

props.content: I you are interested in the remote personal coaching I can provide to you or your organisation please visit the Strive4 Website to learn more about what I can offer.
About Workouts
These YouTube workouts started at the beginning of the 2020 Covid lockdown to replace a local fitness class that I ran.
I started with Monday night workouts, offering a gentle bend and stretch class a 30 min "Green Route" and a more cardio intensive "Red Route".
I then added cardio / circuit workouts on Saturday morning (40mins), Tuesday lunchtime (40mins) and Thursday lunchtimes (30mins).
All the workouts are free and can be done on demand. They require very little in the way of coordination and offer a good range of cardio and body weight exercises.
If you enjoy them and want to donate to my charity website for Cancer Research UK the link is below.
Workout Schedule
